            <p>There is no doubt that Heathrow Airport is one of the busiest in the world, and Terminal 5, or T5 stands out as its most modern and recognizable hub. The terminal opened in 2008, and it is a vast and high-tech building that is designed to make travel as smooth as possible for millions of passengers every year. </p>
