            <p>Terminal 5 is a home a dedicated home primarily for <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/british-airways.aspx"><b>British Airways flights</b></a>, along with its sister airline, Iberia. This means if you are flying with British Airways or Iberia to or from Heathrow, there is a high chance that you will be using or flying from T5 of this airport. </p>
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long"></i> Why is it so important? </h3>
